by_statement: Khaṅʻ Saṅʻʺ Krū, pru cu sū.

description.value: On bibliography of all books published in Burma in 1938-1939.

notes.value:
"Cā kraññʻʹ tuikʻ Paññā Dīpaluimā Bhvaiʹ ʼa tvakʻ lui ʼapʻ khyakʻ myāʺ e* tacʻ citʻ tacʻ desa ʼa phracʻ ī kyamʻʺ ṅayʻ kui taṅʻ pra pā saññʻ."

Thesis (Dip. Lib.--Ranʻ kunʻ Takkasuilʻ, 1978).

Includes bibliographical references (p. [201]-[204]) and index.

In Burmese, with some English.
